text: Kiko García (born 25 August 1968) is a Spanish former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics, finishing in 24th place. ==Major results== ;1989 : 1st Overall Clásica de Alcobendas ;1992 : 1st Overall Clásica de Alcobendas ;1993 : 2nd Overall Vuelta a La Rioja ::1st Stage 1 ;1996 : 2nd Clásica Sabiñánigo ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Spain Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Courbevoie
title: Kiko García (cyclist)
